---
title: All-American Chicken & Roast Pumpkin Toss with Onion Chutney & Mayo
description: This heavenly chicken coated in our All-American seasoning is full of flavour, thanks to red capsicum, onion and garlic. Add a medley of veggies, sweet chutney and a dollop of creamy mayo and it’s satisfaction, guaranteed!

